reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 3, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This desk is amazing. It was super easy to put together, very sturdy, looks great, and I love the outlet integration. I’m always worried these products would come with damages, but nothing was dinged or scratched that I know of. OH AND THE FABRIC DRAWERS DO NOT SMELL AT ALL. Maybe it’s just me, but I’ve ordered products with fabric shelves from amazon before and it would have an unpleasant smell to them that don’t go away no matter how much I spray them :’(The desk seems a little short, but I haven’t gone around to get a chair for it yet so that not a big deal. No missing screws and they provide the tools needed to make assembly easy. Oh. There were actually two instances when the screws were a little hard to put in because of the alignment, but a little force allowed for entry. Overall very happy with my beautiful desk with lovely storage space. It was such a good price too.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 3, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Bang for your buck
reviews.reviewText: This was a great buy if you're on a budget. Power strip is a nice added feature. Not too big. I wish it had a raised shelf on the lower side but it's okay. Sturdy. Simple instructions for the most part.... installation may have worked my last nerve. it's a lot to put together but I did it by myself and wasn't anything crazy. I will say, do not tighten any screws all the way until you know you can align all the screws for that piece first..not even a little bit. Getting the desk pieces to align with the screw holes was a bit of a struggle (actually I may have threatened to throw it out a few times lol) and if you had tightened anything, it wouldn't line up. So learn from the person who had to loosen every single screw just to get another one to line up...Sturdy. Metal frame. the top which is a pressed wood I'm assuming but Defintely is not as cheap feeling as I had thought. The drawers are a fabric drawer like you would use in a cube storage so no, they are not going to be good quality drawers but again for the price, it's just fine. Can be put together in two separate styles. Definitely worth the price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Better than expected
reviews.reviewText: The desk is sturdy, the assembly is straight forward, and it looks great.I was expecting a flimsy aluminum alloy, cheap press board, and brittle screws. But everything is much higher quality than that. It feels like a more expensive desk, which is great.One thing to note, the arrangement of the desk is not as customizable as I was hoping. The desk only has two configurations, either straight or L shaped, and its not like the seller promised more than that. But the way it's designed, the shorter desk is always going to be on the left side no matter which side you arrange the taller desk. I was hoping to be able to switch it around at my convenience. I had already made a floor plan with this desk in mind, but that limitation really threw a wrench into the works. However, it was redeemable.The desk doesn't take up too much space at all, and it's still has a decent surface area to work on. Because of that, I was able to change up my floor plan to accommodate the desk without any major issues.Overall, a really good product.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 21, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This is a good, sturdy desk that was easy to assemble and great for the money. I only wish that the drawers were "real" instead of cloth.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 11, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good materials and fairly easy to build
reviews.reviewText: Here’s some things to take note of:Be sure to not mix up A & B screws when building and also I took extra time to look at the angles of the desk in the instruction guide and still ended up building the railing for the drawers wrong, so be cautious of that. Overall a good sturdy desk, it works for consolidating my desk and vanity into one and also has good storage.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Office Desk
reviews.reviewText: For me this is a very good office desk. It was easy to assemble, it’s very sturdy, and the low price was unbelievable. I’ve been on the lookout for an office desk for over a year and this one checked all the boxes for me.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great customer service
reviews.reviewText: We purchase two of these desks for our daughters for Christmas. Unfortunately, one arrived damaged. Instead of returning it to Amazon, I worked with the contact at SUPERJARE to get it resolved. They made it very easy to resolve the issue. Good product, easy to assemble. My girls are happy with the new work space to draw or do homework.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars the desk itself is great, the company seemed a little sketchy...
reviews.reviewText: basically, i ordered the desk, and on the day it was supposed to arrive, i checked the amazon app and it hadnt even shipped yet. i was confused, but shrugged and waited another day. late into the day after it was supposed to come, it still hadnt been shipped. at this point, i was sick of waiting and just wanted a desk. so i requested to cancel this order so i could just get my money back and buy a different deskthey immediately denied my request. then 10 minutes later, i got a notification that the desk is shipping out... a little sketchy, but ok, im glad its finally on its waysetup was easy, they say you need two people but i did it by myself in maybe an hour and a half. one of the surfaces came with a couple of white scratches which im not a fan of but its possible that happened in shipping or while i was reaching into the box and moving things aroundit fits perfectly in my space and im pretty happy with it. overall, i guess i cant complain. im just taking a couple stars off for the company's weird behavior

reviews.reviewTitle: Buena calidad y fácil de armar
reviews.reviewText: Está excelente por su precio.Llevaba meses buscando algún escritorio para mi computadora y este resultó ser mi mejor opción tanto por precio como por diseño y tamaño.Llevo varios meses con él y sigo encantado.
